{
  "stem": "25835.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this-- if you want to talk about the uprising-- it happened on Friday, 1st of August, in 1944.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have 30-something on the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't move to place where I should be with my group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I stay in [NON-ENGLISH] street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then, in our basement, because it was a very big basement under this church, this Greco-Catholic church, they brought wounded boys.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Boys because uprising was mostly young people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They brought-- and gradually, when bombarding finished with buildings, everybody was in basements because no place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Our house also was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And these wounded people came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were brought to basement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I helped them, changing [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this gauze on the wound.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it was very simple, lack of material for nursing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember that my mother brought our linen from upstair because was destroyed, this house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we cut for small pieces as bandages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then we use it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I-- my, my hand-- my book-- not book, my sock like this one from school, I use as first aid.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I put a Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was running from basement to basement to help because many people was-- who were very wounded and very sick.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My knowledge of this, it was [LAUGHS] not too good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I-- now I can smile only how I did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I wanted to help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was-- it the-- it was till moment when uprising, this part of town, old town, was taken by German people, German soldier.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But mostly, it was not German-- Lithuanian or Ukrainian, who joined on the side of Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They came like animal, probably under influence of something, alcohol or drugs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because they were so cruel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They took everybody from this basement.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
